{"tid":1473870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假五大訴求聯署！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:44:36.000Z","uid":28694,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"468e8323abd1558c378520b8f4f52c3f7605642a","tid":1473870,"uid":28694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:33:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">假聯署</span></span></strong><br />\n同身邊嘅人講「唔好簽」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發現【假】五大訴求聯署<br />\n好多人冇睇內文中伏<br />\n內文話要政府做出五大訴求，然而五大訴求係要求政府嚴正執法鎮壓運動！<br />\n<br />\n文宣組唔該幫手宣揚呢個聯署係假嘅（內文係支持政府鎮壓）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/香港受夠了-五大訴求-撥亂反正-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%97%E5%A4%A0%E4%BA%86-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%92%A5%E4%BA%82%E5%8F%8D%E6%AD%A3-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=5de7855f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/香港受夠了-五大訴求-撥亂反正-enough-for-hong-kong-5-demands-to-restore-law-and-order</a><br />\n<br />\n對家仲諗住登報紙聲稱好多人支持，已經有幾萬人簽咗！<br />\n另外中共開始用三毛四方八面入侵，話示威者暴力同滿口謊言，文宣一定要大大力咁還擊！否則後果不堪設想！<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n唔好簽！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經有5萬幾人簽咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681f5f65afe7befe440bf96a432a0b2e78383178","tid":1473870,"uid":28694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrueAUs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrueAUs.png&h=46452